{"tid":1389003,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"實時夢境 適合發夢唔用力嘅您","createTime":"2019-07-30T20:12:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T11:41:06.000Z","uid":208419,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"dfe83fbbd2e5187751b4e271c9ce3cbbb913748d","tid":1389003,"uid":208419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T20:12:45.000Z","msg":"Google 嘅 My map (我的地圖）<br />\n手機或者電腦都做到 用法係加標記同畫線條 就可以同人分享你發夢嘅即時資訊<br />\n<br />\n夢境例子一：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SwEHa3o.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSwEHa3o.png&h=50d73158&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n只要分享共用連結 就可以無私分享 同其他Google雲端文件一樣 可以分享權限 同其他使用者共建夢境 如下：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ijjgfys.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fijjgfys.png&h=27a8e0cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n你嘅觀眾視覺 如下：<br />\n手機版<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6kuDtUS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6kuDtUS.png&h=54bb9f4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n電腦版<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKDtU0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKDtU0.png&h=c7afa019&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n重要!!! 手機觀眾使用時建議請刪除Google Drive app 因為入連結時會自動開Google Drive app 然後逼你用地圖app開 地圖app冇F5 冇得刷新(Im iPhone user)<br />\n<br />\n簡單嘅分享嚟到呢度 最後補充返 實時夢境並非&lsquo;實時&rsquo; 本人測試過 實時夢境經過修改後 觀眾F5大約過1分鐘多少少先同步到 個人認為接受到"},{"pid":"27bb1f3624663f0a01bfc9b851b44963a7f3a186","tid":1389003,"uid":277342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T11:41:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}